## Usage
```bash
# Gemini
export GEMINI_API_KEY=AIzaSyCDrp7d4GUaqkA8Lu3Uc9RDis0LFjpVo6U

# GHL
export GHL_API_KEY=pit-02f417f4-8dcd-4794-a8ce-bdc507a926bb
export GHL_LOCATION_ID=yrvzyq2jB2me4Z23PFxP

# Supabase (ADD THESE)
export SUPABASE_URL=https://[YOUR-PROJECT].supabase.co
export SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=[YOUR-SERVICE-ROLE-KEY]
export SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=[YOUR-ANON-KEY]
```

Or set in environment:
```bash
echo 'export GEMINI_API_KEY=AIzaSyCDrp7d4GUaqkA8Lu3Uc9RDis0LFjpVo6U' >> ~/.zshrc
echo 'export GHL_API_KEY=pit-02f417f4-8dcd-4794-a8ce-bdc507a926bb' >> ~/.zshrc
echo 'export SUPABASE_URL=https://[YOUR-PROJECT].supabase.co' >> ~/.zshrc
echo 'export SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY=[YOUR-KEY]' >> ~/.zshrc
```

